{"tid":1285330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國官員指指供港豬隻離開中國時 沒驗出非洲豬瘟病毒 不猜測是否香港問題","createTime":"2019-07-04T13:59:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T12:45:12.000Z","uid":133680,"like":2,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"cd2c5b0aedb4d3f14bf34c23a9e3b108056794de","tid":1285330,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:59:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/420361564693683/posts/2452796044783548/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F420361564693683%2Fposts%2F2452796044783548%2F&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=43b15853\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/420361564693683/posts/2452796044783548/</a><br />\n<br />\n【農業農村部指供港豬隻離開中國時 沒驗出非洲豬瘟病毒】<br />\n<br />\n本港5月爆出兩宗非洲豬瘟個案，當局指涉事的豬隻都是來自中國。在北京，中國農業農村部副部長于康震指，自去年8月中國爆發非洲豬瘟疫情以來，供港豬隻離開中國時，都沒有驗出有非洲豬瘟病毒。<br />\n<br />\n至於離開中國到了香港以後檢出非洲豬瘟的情況，于康震稱還在分析。當被追問是香港的問題，還是可能運輸上出現問題時，于康震表示：「我不知道，我不猜測。」<br />\n<br />\n全文︰<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/07-04-2019/54107\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F07-04-2019%2F54107&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=845fbf58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/07-04-2019/54107</a><br />\n<br />\n#非洲豬瘟<br />\n<br />\n請支持PassionPrime：<br />\n<a href=\"http://passiontimes.hk/prime/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2Fprime%2F&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=770d9855\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://passiontimes.hk/prime/</a><br />\n<br />\n請支持熱血時報印刷版︰<br />\n<a href=\"http://passiontimes.hk/4.0/regform.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2F4.0%2Fregform.php&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=55c6295c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://passiontimes.hk/4.0/regform.php</a><br />\n<br />\n請支持熱血文青課金計劃：<br />\n<a href=\"htt